hplayer/ herunter','Author: %1$s (IP address: %2$s, %3$s)'=>'Autor: %1$s (IP-Adresse: %2$s, %3$s)','Website: %1$s (IP address: %2$s, %3$s)'=>'Website: %1$s (IP-Adresse: %2$s, %3$s)','Post custom field name%s:'=>'%s:','oEmbed Response'=>'oEmbed-Antwort','oEmbed Responses'=>'oEmbed-Antworten','Method \'%s\' must be overridden.'=>'Die Methode ‚%s‘ muss überschrieben werden.','Hi,

